sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as 👤 User
    participant Menu as 📋 Context Menu
    participant BG as ⚙️ Background SW
    participant TGAPI as 📑 Tab Groups API
    participant TabsAPI as 🔖 Tabs API
    participant CS as 📄 Content Scripts
    participant API as 🔌 BobaAPIClient
    participant qBit as ⬇️ qBitTorrent :8080

    Note over User,qBit: Tab Group Batch Send Flow

    User->>Menu: Right-click on Tab Group
    activate Menu
    Menu-->>User: Show context menu<br/>"Send all torrents to qBit"
    User->>Menu: Select batch send option
    Menu->>BG: contextMenus.onClicked<br/>{menuItemId, parentMenuItemId}
    deactivate Menu
    activate BG
    BG->>TGAPI: chrome.tabGroups.query<br/>{title: groupName}
    activate TGAPI
    TGAPI-->>BG: Return group objects[]<br/>with groupId
    deactivate TGAPI
    BG->>TabsAPI: chrome.tabs.query<br/>{groupId: gid}
    activate TabsAPI
    TabsAPI-->>BG: Return tabs[]<br/>with tabId, url
    deactivate TabsAPI

    loop For each tab in group
        BG->>CS: chrome.scripting.executeScript<br/>{target: {tabId}, files: ["content.js"]}
        activate CS
        CS->>CS: Scan DOM for torrents
        CS->>CS: parser.normalizeURLs()
        CS-->>BG: Return [{torrents: [...]}]
        deactivate CS
    end

    BG->>BG: Collect all torrents[]<br/>Flatten & deduplicate
    BG->>API: sendBatch(allTorrents)
    activate API
    API->>API: Build batch request<br/>with auth headers
    API->>qBit: POST /api/v2/torrents/add<br/>urls=magnet1\nmagnet2\n...
    activate qBit
    qBit->>qBit: Process each torrent<br/>in parallel
    qBit-->>API: 200 OK + results[]
    deactivate qBit
    API-->>BG: {added: N, failed: [...]}
    deactivate API
    BG->>BG: Store results in<br/>send_history
    BG-->>User: chrome.notifications<br/>"N torrents added successfully"
    deactivate BG
